  "texts": [
    "This calculation is performed in accordance with Ohm's Law.",
    "The power measurements are executed utilizing a Keysight InfiniiVision MSO-X 2024A oscilloscope.",
    "Two passive probes are attached to the GAP9 test points with the aim of measuring the voltage drop, with their grounds connected together.",
    "A third probe is connected to a GPIO pin of the evaluation board for the purpose of synchronizing the measurements across distinct runs, with its ground connected to the board's ground.",
    "The probes are bandwidth-limited to 20 MHz to minimize noise and ensure a clean signal."
